name: WeLink CLUB PASSPORT
description:
WeLink PASS is a collection of 999 OG NFTs that offer its holders exclusive benefits:

Benefits:

- Revenue share from WeLink

- Special $LINK Airdrop

- Whitelist for future WeLink activities

The WeLink PASS collection has 3 levels of rarity:

- Common (70%) – 1X Revenue Share & Special $LINK Airdrop

- Rare (25%) – 3X Revenue Share & Special $LINK Airdrop

- Legendary (5%) – 12X Revenue Share & Special $LINK Airdrop

Unlock these exclusive features and Stay tuned for more benefits in the future.
